Title: Empyrion - Galactic Survival
Genre: Simulation, sandbox, fps

Year: 2015 
Platform: PC 
Version: Pre-Alpha 5.2.0
Language: English 
Multiplayer: Yes 

System requirements: 
OS: Windows 7/8 / 8.1 x64 
Processor: 2.5 GHz 
Memory: 8 GB RAM

Description: Empyrion - Galactic Survival is a 3D open world, space survival adventure in which you can fly across space and land on planets. Build, explore, fight and survive in a hostile galaxy full of hidden dangers
